quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,6,"As for those who have rejected (these truths), it is all the same whether or not you warn them, for they will not believe.",footnotes:177015:1
  2,7,"Allah has sealed their hearts and their hearing, and a covering has fallen over their eyes. They deserve severe chastisement.",footnotes:177016:1
  2,8,"There are some who say: “We believe in Allah and in the Last Day,” while in fact they do not believe."
  2,9,"They are trying to deceive Allah and those who believe, but they do not realize that in truth they are only deceiving themselves.",footnotes:177017:1
  2,10,"There is a disease in their hearts and Allah has intensified this disease. A painful chastisement awaits them for their lying.",footnotes:177018:1